131
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,400
The drug.

132
00:06:24,010 --> 00:06:25,040
That drug.

133
00:06:30,010 --> 00:06:32,960
Tomorrow is our eighth anniversary.

134
00:06:34,659 --> 00:06:36,400
