135
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:38,830
unforgettable

136
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:41,380
for a lifetime.

137
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:59,340
Li Zhiqing.

138
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,880
Wang Yan is going to make a move on you.

139
00:07:02,900 --> 00:07:04,380
Be careful.

140
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,610
