141
00:07:05,780 --> 00:07:08,120
Tonight is your wedding anniversary.

142
00:07:08,580 --> 00:07:09,690
He will go to you.

143
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:12,840
He hasn't noticed that you have a change of heart, has he?

144
00:07:13,770 --> 00:07:15,580
He's very arrogant.

145
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,460
He thinks I'm completely obedient to him.

146
00:07:18,050 --> 00:07:18,810
Oh, right.

147
00:07:19,170 --> 00:07:20,010
Remember,

148
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:22,320
don't drink anything he gives you.

149
00:07:23,020 --> 00:07:24,450
Okay, I got it.

150
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:35,100
What are you doing here?

151
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,120
I've made up my mind.

152
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:40,140
I agree to the divorce.

153
00:07:40,990 --> 00:07:42,590
