162
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,680
I'll leave with nothing.

163
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:05,780
I'll leave Jia with you too.

164
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,040
I'll sign the agreement as you wish.

165
00:08:22,690 --> 00:08:24,430
[Husband's signature: Wang Yan]

166
00:08:29,260 --> 00:08:30,560
[Divorce Agreement]

167
