to commemorate

186
00:09:18,140 --> 00:09:19,540
our lost love

187
00:09:21,020 --> 00:09:22,730
and our completely ended marriage.

188
00:09:24,290 --> 00:09:25,090
Cheers.

189
00:09:28,870 --> 00:09:29,810
Remember,

190
